             was indicted for <rs id="t17890909-147-off725" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17890909-147-off725" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17890909-147-off725" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t17890909-147-cd726" type="crimeDate">3d of August</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17890909-147-off725 t17890909-147-cd726"></join> last, a silver watch, value 40 s. a steel chain, value 6 d. a silver seal, value 8 d. a cornelian seal set in silver, value 6 d. a key, value 2 d. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17890909-147-victim1264" type="victimName">
